                <h1>The Riddler: Batman's Mastermind of Puzzles</h1>
                <p>The Riddler, known as Edward Nygma, is a classic villain from Batman's universe. Famous for his penchant for puzzles and riddles, he challenges the Dark Knight with mind-bending clues. With a complex psyche, he embodies not just a criminal but a symbol of intellect gone awry, captivating fans through comic books, films, and games.</p>
